://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9094488886488306e-48, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's crazy.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those guys are legends.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Legends of their own sport,\\\" said the youngster whose coach, Bob Bowman, also worked with Phelps.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.5961601583758127, \"rank\": 0.6773458377580253, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 876, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999831303957337, \"rank\": 1.6867836476447633e-05, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999941023816, \"rank\": 5.8860533231464295e-09, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just crazy to be compared to those guys.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think I realize from now.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe I will in a few days.\\\"\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand started the Games as a poster boy for the host nation's dreams and aspirations - a hero without any medals to his name, however.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not have long to wait.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold came in the first race, the 400 Individual Medley, and the Frenchman then pulled off the unprecedented feat of the 200 butterfly and breaststroke on the same day.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday he added the 200 Individual Medley.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This morning I woke up and I was full of energy,\\\" Marchand told reporters.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think anything went wrong this week.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been perfect.\\\"\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Four gold medals is not what I thought I could possibly do,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was trying to win one at first.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had four chances of doing it.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I need this time to think about what I just did, for sure.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I need a vacation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bowman said comparisons with Phelps were justified.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999831303957337, \"rank\": 1.6867836476447633e-05, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"