Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's becoming a sort of global superstar now,\\\" said the Scot.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He kind of runs France now\\u2026 you can see he's doing it with a smile on his face and the crowd's giving him so much energy.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2316, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7682330237639268, \"rank\": 0.14326522647984208, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been amazing to witness.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": []}]}"